HEADWORD: Dowitcher
<hw>Dow"itch*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>The red-breasted or gray snipe (<spn>Macrorhamphus griseus</spn>);
-- called also <altname>brownback</altname>, and
<altname>grayback</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
